ZLIB for Cell, provided here has been extended from the ZLIB library  and optimized for the IBM Cell Broadband Engine.  This extension has been programmed by Seunghwa Kang and David A. Bader. ZLIB version 1.2.3 (available at http://www.zlib.net/) has been used as the base library for this extension.

